WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:10.802
Well, good morning, family. Praise the Lord. Thank you for joining us again today. It's not morning, but almost.

00:00:10.803 --> 00:00:33.671
It's pretty late at night, but I just wanted to come on and pray with you all a little bit tonight before you all go to bed, praying over your week that you will have a victorious week, that this week will be a week of breakthrough for your household, and that we're closing out 2025 not broke, busted, and disgusted, but believing God for the overflow.

00:00:33.672 --> 00:00:41.271
You know, I told you all, make that list and stretch your faith. You need spiritual stretch marks.

00:00:41.272 --> 00:00:51.079
I've talked about it how many times now—that you are believing God so big, but you're so pregnant spiritually that you have spiritual stretch marks.

00:00:51.080 --> 00:00:56.768
It's time to believe God for the exceedingly abundantly above all that you dare ask or think.

00:00:56.769 --> 00:01:14.439
That's where I said, "Let's finish 2025 with the overflow."When the Lord is showing us in the vision to believe for your house to be paid off, believe for your student loans, believe for your car note to be paid off, and to be debt-free.

00:01:14.440 --> 00:01:20.934
We have about eight weeks left of this year, and it's nothing for God.

00:01:20.935 --> 00:01:28.799
I just know He can turn it on a dime, and there's a million and one ways that He can get you a million dollars. I just believe it.

00:01:28.800 --> 00:01:39.985
And you say, "Well, Brandon, why are you saying all that?"Because He's been stretching me to believe Him for bigger and to have spiritual stretch marks.

00:01:39.986 --> 00:01:46.795
If you don't have spiritual stretch marks, you're not believing big enough because you're not pregnant enough with what God has called you to do.

00:01:46.796 --> 00:01:53.199
You're not stretching out there knowing that God is able to do it.

00:01:53.200 --> 00:02:00.045
If you're just barely believing, that's where you're going to be; you're just going to barely get by and barely hit the status quo.

00:02:00.046 --> 00:02:09.909
But if you're believing for big, I would rather believe for huge and get half of it than believe for small and get nothing.

00:02:09.910 --> 00:02:23.559
Believe for an overflow so big that you go, "Man, I'm not only believing for my house to be paid off, but I'm going to pay off my pastor's house."Why not believe big?

00:02:23.560 --> 00:02:29.999
I've got so much overflow to have my stuff paid off that I've got enough to pay off three other people's stuff.

00:02:30.000 --> 00:02:35.159
I'm a lender unto many, and I shall not borrow. Why not believe for big?

00:02:35.160 --> 00:02:45.239
So, I set out to believe for big things for the rest of the year going into 2026. What are you believing God for in 2026?

00:02:45.240 --> 00:02:51.017
I'm believing for my kids to be saved, I'm believing for my wife to be saved, and I'm believing for my husband to be saved.

00:02:51.018 --> 00:02:59.488
I want to walk in the supernatural. Why not? Why not you? Why not me?

00:02:59.489 --> 00:03:03.908
There's an expiration date to your problems. That's where I was at today.

00:03:03.909 --> 00:03:11.831
Guys, I was blowing the leaves off in my yard and cleaning up my yard today because the leaves are falling so heavily now.

00:03:11.832 --> 00:03:19.467
It's starting to rain leaves here in Tulsa, and the leaves are saying hello.

00:03:19.468 --> 00:03:26.966
I told Diana I don't like this part of the year whenever these leaves are doing all that, but it's a blessing, and we're so thankful for the trees.

00:03:26.967 --> 00:03:33.134
I just want to say that to you all just to stretch yourself to believe.

00:03:33.135 --> 00:03:42.128
When I was outside and I was doing the yard work, prayer tonight was at the church, and Pastor Candace and them always have prayer.

00:03:42.129 --> 00:03:48.903
I was like, "Man, I want to finish these leaves."Then the Lord said, "Brandon, I want you to go to prayer and add your supply.

00:03:48.904 --> 00:03:52.780
I want you to take your family, and I want you to add your supply.

00:03:52.781 --> 00:04:00.313
There's things that I'll show you in reward if you go. I want you to add your supply."So I said, "Okay, Father.

00:04:00.314 --> 00:04:06.145
I'll do it."I love prayer anyway; it's not like you have to twist my arm to go pray.

00:04:06.146 --> 00:04:21.047
