00:04:42.831 --> 00:04:50.239
I believe there's an anointing for that—to pray for certain things that God calls your vein of what you're to pray for.

00:04:50.240 --> 00:05:00.848
He shows me a lot about the economy privately that I don't talk about—about the housing market, about gold, about everything—and I just intercede for this.

00:05:00.849 --> 00:05:17.399
So I just started adding my supply, and all of a sudden I was taken in the spirit and saw what the spirit of God was showing me.

00:05:17.400 --> 00:05:36.486
I saw four major, huge doors. They were built on a rock, but it wasn't a normal rock.

00:05:36.487 --> 00:05:52.243
It looked like a white, chalky rock, but it was holy. All these doors were built on this rock.

00:05:52.244 --> 00:06:05.442
I could see each individual one was completely black. Take your screen on your cell phone when it's turned off—that blackness.

00:06:05.443 --> 00:06:14.300
It looks like that; it's piercing, it swallows you, and you get lost in it.

00:06:14.301 --> 00:06:28.768
These doors were so black that you couldn't make out the door handles, but I knew they were separate and individually done.

00:06:28.769 --> 00:06:42.239
The Lord had me praying over these doors, and all of a sudden the middle door opened up, and in this door were golden coins.

00:06:42.240 --> 00:06:53.119
Megan's laughing about those golden coins; she gets excited; she's in the living room. She's fine.

00:06:53.120 --> 00:07:08.842
The golden coins were on a hill, and as the door opened up, they started falling through the door like an avalanche.

00:07:08.843 --> 00:07:25.260
These were all stacked up really high, and as the door opened, it was so full of golden coins that they started coming out because the pressure was on the door.

00:07:25.261 --> 00:07:32.060
I was looking at that door, and the Lord said to pray, because it was so dark that the outside of it was hidden.

00:07:32.061 --> 00:07:38.310
You had to pray into it; you had to contend for it. Like I keep telling y'all, we have to contend for the blessing.

00:07:38.311 --> 00:07:46.119
You cannot just idly sit by and expect to walk in the abundance for these last days.

00:07:46.120 --> 00:07:56.169
