00:07:56.170 --> 00:08:05.119
So we are going and plundering the demonic realm and saying, "Listen, we're taking back what you stole from us.

00:08:05.120 --> 00:08:22.712
We're taking back everything the devil has stolen from us, and we're demanding the thief pay us double for our trouble."I'm calling for double for my trouble—everything that you have been stealing from me for how many years.

00:08:22.713 --> 00:08:27.809
Then the Lord said, "Call for your ancestors'finances."We were praying into this.

00:08:27.810 --> 00:08:37.319
I haven't even brought this up yet. But the Lord said to us, "Call for your ancestors'seeds, too.

00:08:37.320 --> 00:08:49.430
If your family generation worked hard, sowed, and were givers at their church but they never reaped it, he said, 'Call for their seeds, too.

00:08:49.431 --> 00:08:56.820
If they never reaped it, those seeds do not die.'"Seeds do not die.

00:08:56.821 --> 00:09:05.558
He said, "They lie dormant sometimes in the ground or, if they're in a dark place, they won't grow until the light hits them or unless water hits them.

00:09:05.559 --> 00:09:11.559
You can put seed in there."He said, "Speak to those old seeds to reap a harvest, Brandon.

00:09:11.560 --> 00:09:35.953
For there's generational wealth that is coming for the body of Christ if you lay hold to it, for this last outpouring of finances, for an end-time harvest transfer."Sister Billye said, "I didn't know if it was biblical or not."She said that because you always want to know if you're off.

00:09:35.954 --> 00:09:41.199
If it's not in the Word, you cannot go against what the Word says.

00:09:41.200 --> 00:09:53.111
So Sister Billye Brim, who wrote this book we were talking about yesterday that Diana read—she's an elder and I always respect my elders.

00:09:53.112 --> 00:10:02.318
She started researching all the biblical basis for an end-time wealth transfer and she says it's in the Word.

00:10:02.319 --> 00:10:07.834
She found it all. She goes through the Greek; she's brilliant when it comes to this stuff.

00:10:07.835 --> 00:10:18.736
I love it when you can talk to her and have a really cool conversation about the Word; she's full of the Word. The end-time wealth transfer is there.

00:10:18.737 --> 00:10:30.472
As I was praying into this—and maybe we'll have her on one day and she can talk about it because you want to know where that's at in the Word—I'm not educated enough to tell you.

00:10:30.473 --> 00:10:45.881
I'm humble enough to tell you that I don't know, but I trust her and I'll allow her to come on and show you in the Word where it's at because I thought it was awesome.

00:10:45.882 --> 00:11:02.039
She had it all in there. Going back to the doors: I saw these four doors and as I was praying, the Lord said, "These are end-time. This is what's hidden. It's in the darkness.

00:11:02.040 --> 00:11:18.159
You have to pray and contend for it and bring it out into the light."As you are praying, I saw the gold door open and all this coin, and then I saw silver open and the silver started to fall out. I said, "What are the other two doors?"I don't know yet.

00:11:18.160 --> 00:11:32.119
But as I was praying, the Lord was showing me—and this is not financial advice, I'm not telling you to buy silver or gold—I'm telling you what I saw behind the door and what I'm praying over.

00:11:32.120 --> 00:11:38.269
