00:11:38.270 --> 00:11:44.239
As I was praying, I saw these doors open. Then I saw two doors over here and they represented something.

00:11:44.240 --> 00:11:56.312
But as I was praying, I could see these four electric lines on an electric pole.

00:11:56.312 --> 00:12:05.519
What was interesting was the electric pole was blacked out so much that you could not really make out that it was an electric pole.

00:12:05.520 --> 00:12:17.863
The electric lines were like lines you see on the earth running to—I was trying to show them like a black extension cord—but they were like a black cord.

00:12:17.864 --> 00:12:24.838
It's all right, son. It's a black cord that was running and powering each door.

00:12:24.839 --> 00:12:35.036
And the Lord said, "Flip the switch. Flip the switch."I started interceding for this.

00:12:35.037 --> 00:12:44.386
When I started seeing this black cord—thanks, Braden. Black headphones. You can have them back, buddy. Thank you.

00:12:44.387 --> 00:12:52.339
As I was praying, the Lord said, "Pray into this."I get these assignments and I'm like a boy.

00:12:52.340 --> 00:13:00.073
The lady up at the front is leading and going a totally different direction, but I'm in the back with my heels ground down in the ground.

00:13:00.074 --> 00:13:10.159
