00:13:24.355 --> 00:13:28.816
Their noses are to the ground and they're going to find out what this is in the spirit realm.

00:13:28.817 --> 00:13:35.639
That's just the way I am because I am determined to have everything that God has for me.

00:13:35.640 --> 00:13:40.732
I am determined to make sure I don't lack any good thing for my family.

00:13:40.733 --> 00:13:50.393
We are going to be on that side of the blessing, that side of exceedingly abundantly. We have what it takes to do it. We're contenders.

00:13:50.394 --> 00:13:57.392
The Lord told me on the way home, I told her, I said, "Do we do a live stream tonight?"because it was late already.

00:13:57.393 --> 00:14:03.999
I said, "You know, there are certain things I could have done, but let's pray some more about these doors.

00:14:04.000 --> 00:14:22.715
